@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
title 09. Supervisor Agent Security Model (Python runtime)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

rectangle "Input Guard" {
  [supervisor_a2a_endpoint] as Controller
  [supervisor_a2a_request_validator] as Validator
  [prompt_injection_guard] as PromptGuard
}

rectangle "Task / Review Ownership Guard" {
  [supervisor_agent_service] as Service
  [supervisor_a2a_lifecycle_service] as Lifecycle
  [hitl_decision_service] as HitlDecision
}

rectangle "Routing & Invocation Guard" {
  [A2AClientRegistry] as Registry
  [Allowed Route Config] as Allowlist
  [default_a2a_invocation_service] as Invoker
  [handoff_policy_service] as HandoffPolicy
  [Allowed Method Guard] as MethodGuard
  [Streaming Capability Guard] as StreamGuard
  [Retry/Timeout Policy] as RetryTimeout
  [Circuit Breaker] as CircuitBreaker
}

rectangle "State Integrity" {
  [supervisor_swarm_coordinator] as SwarmCoordinator
  [Swarm State Version Check] as SwarmVersion
  [Review Store] as ReviewStore
}

rectangle "Error Safety" {
  [supervisor_exception_handler] as ErrorHandler
}

Controller --> Validator : method/params/schema
Controller --> PromptGuard : sanitize message text
Validator --> Service : normalize text/A2UI userAction
Service --> Lifecycle : session-owned task read/cancel/list
Service --> HitlDecision : session-owned review get/decide
Invoker --> Registry : resolve target
Registry --> Allowlist : validate agent key / endpoint / method
Invoker --> RetryTimeout : bounded retry/backoff
Invoker --> CircuitBreaker : fail-fast on repeated errors
HandoffPolicy --> MethodGuard : allowMethods check
HandoffPolicy --> StreamGuard : downstream stream support check
SwarmCoordinator --> SwarmVersion : optimistic lock + retry
HitlDecision --> ReviewStore : session-bound review ownership
ErrorHandler --> Invoker : sanitize runtime failures

note right of Validator
Current input handling
- legacy messageText
- v1.0 message.parts[].text
- application/json+a2ui userAction
- invalid decision values rejected before service
end note

note right of HandoffPolicy
Current handoff hardening
- feature flag
- route allowlist only
- method allowlist only
- recent path duplicate block
- max hops
end note

note bottom of ErrorHandler
No sensitive leak
- internal stack traces
- downstream raw HTTP details
- credentials / provider internals
end note
@enduml
